quran[7{c,v,t}:
49,12,ae ahal imaan! bohat gumaan karne se Ihtiraz karo ke baaz gumaan gunah hain. aur aik dosray ke haal ka tajassus nahkiya karo aur nah koi kisi ki gheebat kere.kiya tum mein se koi is baat ko pasand kere ga ke apne marey hue bhai ka gosht khaye? is se to tum zaroor nafrat karo ge. ( to gheebat nah karo ) aur khuda ka dar rakho be shak khuda tauba qubool karne wala meharban hai
49,13,logo! hum ne tum ko aik mard aur aik aurat se pedakiya aur tumhari qoumain aur qabeeley banaye. taakay aik dosray ko shanakht karo. aur khuda ke nazdeek tum mein ziyada izzat wala woh hai jo ziyada parhaizgaar hai. be shak khuda sab kuch jan-nay wala ( aur ) sab se khabardaar hai
49,14,dehati kehte hain ke hum imaan le aeye. keh do ke tum imaan nahi laaye ( balkay yun ) kaho ke hum islam laaye hain aur imaan to hunooz tumahray dilon mein daakhil hi nahi howa. aur tum khuda aur is ke rasool ki farmabardari karo ge to khuda tumahray aamaal se kuch kam nahi kere ga. be shak khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
49,15,momin to woh hain jo khuda aur is ke rasool par imaan laaye phir shak mein nah parre aur khuda ki raah mein maal aur jaan se larray. yahi log ( imaan ke ) sachey hain
49,16,un se kahokiya tum khuda ko apni deendari jatlatay ho. aur khuda to asmano aur zameen ki sab cheezon se waaqif hai. aur khuda har shai ko jaanta hai
49,17,yeh log tum par ahsaan rakhtay hain ke musalman hogaye hain. keh do ke apne musalman honay ka mujh par ahsaan nah rakho. balkay khuda tum par ahsaan rakhta hai ke is ne tumhe imaan ka rasta dekhaya bashart e kay tum sachey ( musalman ) ho
49,18,be shak khuda asmano aur zameen ki posheeda baton ko jaanta hai aur jo kuch tum karte ho usay daikhta hai
